window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The world will burn in the final installment of Scarlett St. Clair's bestselling Hades X Persephone saga.</p> <p>The gods are at war, the Titans have been released, and Hades and Persephone must fight tooth and nail for their happy ending.</p> <p>Persephone, Goddess of Spring, never guessed that a chance encounter with Hades, God of the Underworld, would change her life forever—but he did. Now embroiled in a fight for humanity and battles between the gods, Persephone and Hades have entered a world they never thought they would see. To end the chaos, Persephone must draw upon her darkness and embrace who she's become—goddess, wife, queen of the Underworld.</p> <p>Once, Persephone made bargains to save those she loves. Now, she will go to war for them.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
